# Feature delivery

## Before implementing

1. Read all relevant docs completely (Blueprint, Playbook chapter, Prompt Library prompt)
2. Explain: what · why (build order) · files · architectural decisions
3. On doc conflict: stop and explain before coding

## After implementing

- Run tests, `pnpm lint`, `pnpm typecheck` — fix all errors
- Update docs in same change if behaviour changed
- Verify Success Criteria line by line
- Do not start next chapter/prompt until stable

## Per feature response

Approach → why → code → file locations → testing

No placeholder implementations unless unavoidable.
